\r\n','It aims to provide the most compelling range of content and services in Bristol; comprehensive what\'s on listings and recommendations; mixed media marketing packages at highly cost-effective prices, providing a digital shop window for local businesses.\r\n\r\nTwice voted EDF Energy South West Website of the Year, the new B247 comes to you across a range of different media: \r\n\r\n- A FREE monthly magazine distributed across Bristol\r\n- A revamped, responsive website you can personalise to suit your own tastes\r\n- A mobile/tablet app providing alerts and offers \r\n\r\nWe provide high-quality, independent news and features from our team of experienced and talented journalists and bloggers. Our ethos is to be independent, honest and transparent, and uphold the highest editorial values. You can read our editorial vision here… [link]\r\n\r\nWe aim to provide Bristol businesses with a range of great-value, innovative marketing packages across our print and digital platforms to help them reach new, trusted audiences. You can find out more about our advertising and marketing offers here… [link]\r\n\r\nB247 operates as a Community Interest Company (CIC), which means we are duty bound to invest a substantial proportion of our profits and continuing efforts into providing the best service possible for Bristol.\r\n\r\nWe operate with a board of private investors charged with overseeing the operation of the business. You can find out who is on the board here… [link]\r\n\r\nIf you want to find out more about us, please don’t hesitate to contact us at:\r\nT: 0117 300 5526\r\nE: editor@bristol247.com',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),
